The Haskell programmer in me can&#x27;t resist---eta reduce your functions! :P<p><pre><code>    from functools import partial

    def odd_count(letters, ch):
        return letters.count(ch) % 2

    def anagram_of_palindrome(letters):
        return sum(map(partial(odd_count, letters), set(letters))) <= 1</code></pre>
